name: Google Earth VR
description: Performance is poor using the default Proton version. Changing to Proton 4.11-11 dramatically fixes the issues.
notes:
Changing to Proton 4.11-11 
Install game
Find game in library and click the configure icon, select properties
On first tab check box to "Force the use of a specific Steam Compatibility Tool"
Select Proton 4.11-11 (or newer)
